openadk.library.impl
Class ObjectFactory

java.lang.Object
  openadk.library.impl.ObjectFactory
Direct Known Subclasses:
ObjectFactoryImpl
public abstract class ObjectFactory
extends java.lang.Object

Factory for creating objects used by the ADK. The following object are currently created by this class:

  • ZoneFactory (The ZoneFactory used to create zone objects in the ADK)
  • TopicFactory (The Topic factory used by the ADK)

Version:
2.1
Author:
Andrew Elmhorst
